'''塔拉吉·潘妲·漢森'''（{{lang-en|'''Taraji Penda Henson'''}}<ref name="bio">{{cite web|title=Taraji P. Henson - Biography|url=http://www.biography.com/people/taraji-henson-21192695#synopsis|publisher={{link-en|FYI (電視網)|FYI (U.S. TV channel)|Biography.com}} ({{link-en|FYI (電視網)|FYI (U.S. TV channel)|FYI}}／[[A+E電視網|A+E電視網]])|accessdate=2014-09-18|archive-date=2015-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215100103/http://www.biography.com/people/taraji-henson-21192695#synopsis|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=tvg>{{cite web | url = http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/taraji-p-henson-191266/| title=Taraji P. Henson | publisher= [[電視指南|電視指南]] | accessdate= 2014-09-18 | archivedate=2016-03-05 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305215321/http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/taraji-p-henson/191266/ | deadurl=no}}</ref>，{{IPAc-en|t|ə|'|r|ɑː|dʒ|i}} {{respell|tə|RAH|jee}}，{{bd|1970年|9月11日|catidx=Henson}}）<ref name="bio" /><ref name=tvg />是一名美國女演員兼歌手。其於[[霍華德大學|霍華德大學]]修習演藝課程，並展開[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]事業。2016年，〈[[時代_(雜誌)|時代雜誌]]〉將其評選為[[時代百大人物|時代百大人物]]之一。

2008年因演出《[[奇幻逆緣|班傑明的奇幻旅程]]》而入圍了[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]][[奧斯卡最佳女配角獎|最佳女配角]]以及[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]][[美國演員工會獎最佳女配角|最佳女配角]]。2011年憑《{{link-en|悍母救援|Taken from Me: The Tiffany Rubin Story}}》首次獲[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]提名；2011年至2013年間，參與了[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]電視劇《[[疑犯追蹤|疑犯追蹤]]》的演出；2015年主演了[[福斯廣播公司|FOX]]人氣劇《[[嘻哈帝國|嘻哈帝國]]》，並獲得評論家的好評，更奪得[[第73屆金球獎|第73屆金球獎]]最佳電視劇情類影集女演員獎及{{link-en|評論家選擇電視獎|Critics' Choice Television Award}}劇情類影集最佳女演員獎，同時入圍了兩屆黃金時段艾美獎最佳劇情類影集女主角獎。2017年憑《[[隱藏人物|關鍵少數]]》獲得首座[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]。

其深受[[有色人種促進協會形象獎|有色人種促進協會形象獎]]的喜愛，至今入圍了10項獎項，並抱回了7項獎座。

== 早年生活與學業 ==
漢森出生於[[美國|美國]][[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|華盛頓哥倫比亞特區]]，母親柏妮絲（{{lang|en|Bernice}}）任職於{{link-en|伍德沃與羅斯洛|Woodward & Lothrop}}，父親布利斯·勞倫斯·漢森（{{lang|en|Boris Lawrence Henson}}）則為一名金屬製造商門警。<ref>{{cite web|title=Boris Lawrence Henson RIP...I no u got heaven in stitches cause u had the best sense of humor even in your last moments you kept us laughin.|url=https://twitter.com/therealtaraji/status/7676062665|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|accessdate=2015-01-10|archive-date=2019-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626224730/https://twitter.com/therealtaraji/status/7676062665|dead-url=no}}</ref> 漢森總是談起外婆帕琪·貝拉德（{{lang|en|Patsy Ballard}}）對自己的影響，而漢森更邀請帕琪和自己一同參加奧斯卡典禮。<ref>[http://content.usatoday.com/communities/entertainment/post/2009/02/63205015/1#.WBuh_CmTus4 Henson interview 2009] {{Wayback|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/entertainment/post/2009/02/63205015/1#.WBuh_CmTus4 |date=20191215123438 }} accessed 11/3/2016</ref><ref name=Wiltz>{{Citation|last = Wiltz|first = Teresa|title = Drama Queen: Taraji Henson Moved to Hollywood And Smacked It Right Upside the Head|newspaper = [[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]|page = C01|date = 2005-07-21|url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/07/20/AR2005072002355.html|accessdate = 2016-12-04|archive-date = 2018-10-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181003180145/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/07/20/AR2005072002355.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.wsj.com/articles/SB123507540420025655 | title = Veteran Actors, First Time Nominees | work = [[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]] | date = 2009-02-19 | accessdate = 2016-12-04 | archive-date = 2019-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190925190302/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB123507540420025655 | dead-url = no }}{{subscription}}</ref><ref>[http://www.njonthego.com/Article.aspx?id=69864 NAACP nominates actress with local ties] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104005942/http://www.njonthego.com/Article.aspx?id=69864 |date=2014-11-04 }}</ref><ref name="thr2008">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-roundtable-actresses-124073 |title=Oscar Roundtable: The Actresses |publisher=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]] |date=2008-12-08 |first1=Stephen |last1=Galloway |first2=Elizabeth |last2=Guider |accessdate=2014-11-03 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103040035/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-roundtable-actresses-124073 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 漢森的名字與中間名是取自[[斯瓦希里語|斯瓦希里語]]，泰拉姬意旨“希望”，“潘妲”則意旨“愛”。<ref name="ReferenceA">{{link-en|泰維斯·斯密利|Tavis Smiley}}採訪, December 19, 2008.</ref><ref>{{cite interview |last = Henson |first = Taraji P. |interviewer = [[大衛·萊特曼|大衛·萊特曼]] |title = [[大衛·萊特曼晚間秀|大衛·萊特曼晚間秀]] |date =2013-12-05 |publisher={{link-en|Worldwide Pants|Worldwide Pants}} }}</ref> 根據[[線粒體DNA|線粒體DNA]]鑑定，她的母系血統可追溯自[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]{{link-en|瑪莎人|Masa people}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9EaKWkmRbbs&feature=relmfu|title=Taraji P. Henson Ancestry Reveal|publisher=The Africa Channel via [[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=2012-01-31|accessdate=2013-01-14|archive-date=2019-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123060931/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9EaKWkmRbbs&feature=relmfu|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她曾說北極探險家{{link-en|麥修·漢森|Matthew Henson}}是她曾曾祖父的兄弟。<ref>{{cite web | url  = http://aalbc.com/reviews/taraji_p_henson.htm | title= Taraji Shares All, Even the Surprising Color of Her Panties| publisher=African American Literature Book Club | first=Kam|last= Williams| date= 2008| accessdate= 2015-04-13| archivedate= 2008-11-21| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081121123915/http://www.aalbc.com/reviews/taraji_p_henson.htm | deadurl=no}}</ref>

漢森在1988年於[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]]{{link-en|奧克森山 (馬里蘭州)|Oxon Hill, Maryland|奧克森山}}之{{link-en|奧克森山高中|Oxon Hill High School}}畢業，<ref name="bio" /> 並於[[北卡羅來納州立農業技術大學|北卡羅來納州立農業技術大學]]主修電子工程，後轉至[[霍華德大學|霍華德大學]]主修戲劇。<ref name=Wiltz /><ref name="thr2008"/> 為了支付大學學費，漢森早上於[[五角大樓|五角大廈]]擔任秘書，晚上則在晚餐郵輪擔任歌舞服務生。<ref name="Meet the Nominees: Taraji P. Henson">{{cite news| url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2009/02/meet-the-nominees-taraji-p-henson| title=Meet the Nominees: Taraji P. Henson| work=[[名利場_(雜誌)|浮華世界]]| date=2009-02-12| first=Andi| last=Teran| accessdate=2015-04-07| archive-date=2015-01-31| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131042712/http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2009/02/meet-the-nominees-taraji-p-henson| dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 事業 ==
=== 電影 ===
漢森在2001年喜劇劇情電影《{{link-en|寶貝男孩|Baby Boy (film)}}》中飾演伊薇特而展露頭角。<ref>{{cite web|title=Taraji P. Henson Talks Cookie Taking Over Her Life, Kerry Washington, Baby Boy Sequel, Season 2 Of Empire + More|url=http://www.power1051fm.com/onair/angie-martinez-54909/taraji-p-henson-talks-cookie-taking-13412740|publisher=power1051fm.com|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402204845/http://www.power1051fm.com/onair/angie-martinez-54909/taraji-p-henson-talks-cookie-taking-13412740|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2005年，漢森於《{{link-en|饒舌歌王|Hustle & Flow}}》中飾演女主角莎格，該電影獲得不錯的評價，並奪得一項[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]。2008年，漢森於《[[奇幻逆緣|班傑明的奇幻旅程]]》中飾演[[畢·彼特|布萊德·彼特]]所扮演之班傑明的養母昆妮，<ref name="kam" /> 並因該劇入圍奧斯卡金像獎[[奧斯卡最佳女配角獎|最佳女配角獎]]。<ref>{{Citation | last = MacDonald |first = Gayle| title=Benjamin Button Leads Race for What Pitt Calls -- Our Highest Honour| newspaper=Globe & Mail |location=Toronto |page= R13.|date= 2009-01-23}}</ref> 她在採訪時說道：「昆妮是無條件愛的體現。」<ref name="ReferenceA"/><ref name="kam">{{cite news |first=Kam |last=Williams |coauthors= |title=Taraji P. Henson: The Curious Case of Benjamin Button Interview |date=2008-12-14 |publisher=KamWilliams.com |url=http://www.kamwilliams.com/2008/12/taraji-p-henson-curious-case-of.html |work= |pages= |accessdate=2009-06-30 |language= |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118231849/http://www.kamwilliams.com/2008/12/taraji-p-henson-curious-case-of.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

於2008年及2009年，她分別演出了[[泰勒·派瑞|泰勒·派瑞]]的兩部作品《{{link-en|家庭紛爭|The Family That Preys}}》以及《{{link-en|我可以自己瘋|I Can Do Bad All by Myself (film)}}》。

2010年，漢森參演了改編自1984年[[小子難纏|同名電影]]的《[[功夫梦|功夫夢]]》，並在商業上獲得了成功。<ref>{{cite news|title=Taraji P. Henson Interview: The Karate Kid, Beijing Culture and Working for Will Smith|url=http://www.pr.com/article/1154|accessdate=2015-03-18|publisher=pr.com|date=2010-06-09|archive-date=2020-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200301220144/https://www.pr.com/article/1154|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年，漢森主演了{{link-en|LMN (電視頻道)|LMN (TV network)|Lifetime Movie Network}}電視電影《{{link-en|悍母救援|Taken from Me: The Tiffany Rubin Story}}》，該劇改編自真人真事，講述一名母親蒂芬妮·盧賓的六歲兒子被親生父親綁架至[[大韓民國|大韓民國]][[首爾|首爾]]，於是她展開一段找尋兒子的旅程。<ref>{{cite news|title=Taken from Me: The Tiffany Rubin Story: TV review [Lifetime]|url=http://entertainmentrealm.com/2011/01/30/taken-from-me-the-tiffany-rubin-story-tv-review-lifetime-movie/|accessdate=2015-03-19|publisher=entertainmentrealm.com|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402114547/http://entertainmentrealm.com/2011/01/30/taken-from-me-the-tiffany-rubin-story-tv-review-lifetime-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其於該劇的表現獲的影評家的讚賞，<ref>{{cite web|title=Taken from Me: The Tiffany Rubin Story|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/taken_from_me_the_tiffany_rubin_story_2010/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812160238/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/taken_from_me_the_tiffany_rubin_story_2010|dead-url=no}}</ref> 並因此入圍了[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Taraji P. Henson|url=http://www.emmys.com/bios/taraji-p-henson|publisher=[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2020-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200424223934/https://www.emmys.com/bios/taraji-p-henson|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年，漢森加入了改編自[[史蒂夫·哈維|史蒂夫·哈維]]著作《{{link-en|男人的上半身去哪了？|Act Like a Lady, Think Like a Man}}》，擁有龐大卡司群的《{{link-en|男人行不行|Think Like a Man}}》，亦參演了2014的續集《{{link-en|男人行不行2|Think Like a Man Too}}》。<ref name="think">{{cite news|title=Production starts on 'Think Like a Man Too'|url=http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/Movies/2013/05/28/Production-starts-on-Think-Like-a-Man-Too/UPI-48371369775541/|accessdate=2013-09-19|newspaper=upi.com|date=2013-05-28|archive-date=2013-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920103133/http://www.upi.com/Entertainment_News/Movies/2013/05/28/Production-starts-on-Think-Like-a-Man-Too/UPI-48371369775541|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，漢森於《{{le|最佳敵人|The Best of Enemies (2019 film)}}》飾演 Ann Atwater。

=== 電視 ===
