521204328/http://www.theroot.com/articles/culture/2015/02/cookie_monster_how_cookie_lyon_became_the_most_compelling_character_on_tv.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=post>{{cite news|title=‘Empire’s’ Cookie Lyon is TV’s best new female character|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/act-four/wp/2015/03/18/empires-cookie-lyon-is-tvs-best-new-female-character/|author=Alyssa Rosenberg|accessdate=2015-04-22|work=華盛頓郵報|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2020-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200302104522/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/act-four/wp/2015/03/18/empires-cookie-lyon-is-tvs-best-new-female-character/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Harris|first1=Aisha|title=Just Give Taraji P. Henson the Emmy Already|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2015/03/18/taraji_p_henson_for_an_emmy_how_cookie_lyon_became_the_most_fascinating.html|accessdate=2015-04-22|publisher=Slate.com|date=2015-03-18|archive-date=2018-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001103630/http://www.slate.com/blogs/browbeat/2015/03/18/taraji_p_henson_for_an_emmy_how_cookie_lyon_became_the_most_fascinating.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 漢森憑藉該劇連續兩屆入圍了[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]，並成為第3位奪得[[金球獎|金球獎]]最佳電視劇情類女演員獎的非裔女演員。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theroot.com/blogs/the_grapevine/2016/01/taraji_p_henson_becomes_3rd_black_woman_to_win_best_actress_tv_drama_golden.html|title=Taraji P. Henson Becomes 3rd Black Woman to Win Golden Globe for Best Actress in TV Drama|date=2016-01-11|first=Yesha|last=Callahan|work={{link-en|The Root (雜誌)|The Root (magazine)|The Root}}|accessdate=2016-01-17|archive-date=2016-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523004759/http://www.theroot.com/blogs/the_grapevine/2016/01/taraji_p_henson_becomes_3rd_black_woman_to_win_best_actress_tv_drama_golden.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

