2014年，漢森宣稱其兒子在10月18日於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[格倫代爾_(加利福尼亞州)|格倫代爾]]的某個臨檢站，遭受警方種族歧視對待，並非法搜查其兒子的轎車。隨後，[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]刊登了一則影片，其顯示馬賽爾違規，並在口頭答應搜車後，在其車內發現了大麻油與大麻，而馬賽爾亦承認在開車前的兩小時有吸食毒品。<ref name=latimes-march2015>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-actress-taraji-p-henson-son-racial-profile-20150327-story.html#navtype=outfit|work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|title=Actress Taraji Henson apologizes to Glendale police for racial profile claims| first= Veronica| last= Rocha| date= 2015-03-27|accessdate=2015-03-28| archivedate= 2015-04-09| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150409093239/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-actress-taraji-p-henson-son-racial-profile-20150327-story.html | deadurl=no}}</ref> 於影片公開後四十分鐘，<ref name=latimes-march2015 /> 漢森後來於[[Instagram|Instagram]]公開向格倫代爾警局致歉，並表示做為一個母親也不輕鬆於警員。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://instagram.com/p/0v0KjQOuFM/|title=#TurningANegativeIntoAPositive #LoveTarajiPHenson|publisher=[[Instagram|Instagram]]|date=2015-03-27|accessdate=2015-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402153245/https://instagram.com/p/0v0KjQOuFM/|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>[http://losangeles.cbslocal.com/2015/03/27/taraji-p-henson-apologizes-for-claiming-glendale-police-racially-profiled-her-son/ "Actress Taraji P. Henson Apologizes For Claiming Glendale Police Racially Profiled Her Son"] {{Wayback|url=http://losangeles.cbslocal.com/2015/03/27/taraji-p-henson-apologizes-for-claiming-glendale-police-racially-profiled-her-son/ |date=20201108092842 }}, CBS Los Angeles, March 27, 2015.</ref>

